snippet.title: Amber Heard Interview - Magic Mike XXL Premiere
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is interviewed at the Premiere of his movie Magic Mike XXL in London.

Magic Mike XXL stars Channing Tatum, Matt Bomer, Joe Manganiello, Gabriel Iglesias, Andie MacDowell, Jada Pinkett Smith, Amber Heard and Elizabeth Banks.
